graph TD
    User([User Device]) -->|HTTPS Request| CDN[Cloud CDN]
    CDN --> Host[Firebase Hosting]
    Host --> Auth[Firebase Authentication]
    Auth --> APIG[API Gateway]
    
    APIG -->|Secured Traffic| CR[Cloud Run - Backend API]
    CR -.->|Fallback / Lightweight| AE[App Engine]
    
    CR -->|Async Tasks| PS[Pub/Sub]
    PS -->|Trigger| CF[Cloud Functions]
    CF -->|Emails / Reminders| FCM[Firebase Cloud Messaging]
    
    CR -->|Read/Write Session| FS[(Firestore)]
    CR -->|Structured Election Data| SQL[(Cloud SQL)]
    CR -->|Document Storage| CS[(Cloud Storage)]
    
    CR -->|Semantic Queries| VertexAI[Vertex AI Gemini]
    CR -->|Voice Analysis| Speech[Cloud Speech-to-Text]
    CR -->|Document Verification| DocAI[Document AI]
    
    CR -->|Analytics Streaming| BQ[(BigQuery)]
    BQ --> Looker[Looker Studio Dashboards]
    
    subgraph DevOps & Security Layer
        IAM[Cloud IAM]
        Secret[Secret Manager]
        Armor[Cloud Armor]
        Build[Cloud Build CI/CD]
        Trace[Cloud Trace / Logging]
    end
    
    Armor --> APIG
    Secret --> CR
